<i>Transmission...</i>

9
00:00:48,880 --> 00:00:50,170
<i>Flammes dévastatrices !</i>

10
00:01:01,180 --> 00:01:02,140
<i>Yûji !</i>

11
00:01:03,430 --> 00:01:05,090
<i>Ç'a pas marché.</i>

